Background
Today, the circuit is as follows - SL import scans, then transmits to CR role (Credit risk) for adjudication, then transmits to SL who transmits to SLA to collect documents, sends to CR to do a final check, before Funders fund who then advises Admin once complete.

However, the real life process is different.   We will have SL import scan (Status Draft), however they will then transmit to SLA (admin) who will then review all the details, send fillable documents etc.

Therefore, we need to update the circuit when application is import scanned.

